- Ability to prevent submitting the form by pressing Enter (e.g. in a textfield).
  I think this can be done with JS (handling onsubmit).
  Alternatively we could handle keypress with the value 13 (but this may be less
  portable).
  See also
  http://kreotekdev.wordpress.com/2007/11/16/disabling-the-enter-key-on-forms-using-javascript/

- Loops with templates using CGI::SSI module.

- Ability to prevent multiple submission of the form (pressing submit button
  several times). See also
  http://worthposting.wordpress.com/2008/07/10/button-submit-once/